app.title: Gerador e validador de CPF Open-Source | Tiago Porto
app.description: Gerador e validador de CPF, open-source JS lib to generate and validate CPF.

header.libInfo: JS open-source lib to generate and validate CPF.

info.disclaimer: Lib available to assist developers in software testing, doesn't have link with "Receita Federal do Brasil".
info.cpfByState: The last digit before verifiers (last 2 digits), corresponds with the brasilian state were CPF was issued.
info.example: Example: CPF <0>XXX.XXX.XX8-XX</0>, number 8 corresponds to São Paulo state.
info.stateCode1: 1. Distrito Federal, Goiás, Mato Grosso do Sul and Tocantins;
info.stateCode2: 2. Pará, Amazonas, Acre, Amapá, Rondônia and Roraima;
info.stateCode4: 4. Pernambuco, Rio Grande do Norte, Paraíba and Alagoas;
info.stateCode7: 7. Rio de Janeiro and Espírito Santo;
info.disclaimerValidCPF: Valid CPF doesn't mean is registered or is active. For those informations, check <0>Secretaria da Receita Federal do Brasil</0>.
